B.au3=new A.cw("What is TableLab?","TableLab is a poker tracking and analysis app for serious players. Log every session you play, review performance trends, record and replay hands for study, build a personal database of opponent reads, and get AI-powered coaching \u2014 all synced to the cloud across devices.")
B.auz=new A.cw("Do I need an account to use the app?","Yes. TableLab uses a secure cloud backend so your data is always backed up and accessible from any device. You can sign in with Google (one tap) or create a traditional email/password account.")
B.auG=new A.cw("How do I navigate the app?","The bottom navigation bar has five tabs: Dashboard, Sessions, Hands, Reads, and Calendar. Tap the menu icon (\u2630) in the top-left of any screen to open the side drawer. The drawer contains your profile, Help, About, Data & Privacy, and the Tools section (Equity Calculator and ICM Deal Calculator).")
B.auk=new A.cw("Is my data private?","Yes. Every query to the database enforces Row-Level Security \u2014 meaning you can only ever read or write your own data. No other user can see your sessions, hands, or reads.")
B.a3a=s([B.au3,B.auz,B.auG,B.auk],t.Bt)
